text: CYM or Cym may refer to: ==Organisations== * Connolly Youth Movement, an Irish socialist youth group * Centre for Young Musicians, London * Spilka Ukraïns'koï Molodi (Спілка української молоді), the Ukrainian Youth Association * CYM RFC, a Rugby Club in Dublin, Ireland ==Standardised codes== * Cayman Islands, by ISO 3166-1 country code * Welsh language or Cymraeg, by ISO 639 language code * .cym, an unused top-level Internet domain * Chatham Seaplane Base, United States, by IATA airport code ==Other uses== * Cym, the Cymbidium orchid genus * CYM, the CMYK color model, in printing
title: CYM
